,p_name=>'PA.APP.DESC.7930'
,p_message_text=>'<p>See how you can create wizards with Oracle Application Express (APEX).  Demonstrates core APEX features including automatic session state management, page branching, and referencing session state with bind variables.  This application also demonst'
||'rates user interface controls including wizard progress trains, buttons, and item labels.</p>'
